### Get All Static Hosts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/static/hosts
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkhlbnJpcXVlIEp1bmciLCJncm91cHMiOlsiZGhjcDphZG1pbiJdLCJpYXQiOjE1MTYyMzkwMjJ9.oQTSWBE48XpiRYO03hl_DNlHAL_ffenf--wlhPJoLPU

